 (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\platform-capability-template.json`)\n163: - `platform-capability-check.md`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\platform-capability-check.md`)\n164: - `platform-capability-check.json`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\platform-capability-check.json`)\n165: - `platform-capability-check-report.md`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\platform-capability-check-report.md`)\n166: - `platform-capability-check-report.json`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\platform-capability-check-report.json`)\n167: - `capability-sdk-probe-cache.md`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\capability-sdk-probe-cache.md`)\n168: - `capability-sdk-probe-cache.json`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\capability-sdk-probe-cache.json`)\n169: - `target-structure-report.md`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\target-structure-report.md`)\n170: - `target-structure-report.json`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\target-structure-report.json`)\n171: - `resource-coverage-report.md`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\resource-coverage-report.md`)\n172: - `resource-coverage-report.json`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\resource-coverage-report.json`)\n173: - `coverage-gap-report.md`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\coverage-gap-report.md`)\n174: - `coverage-gap-report.json`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\coverage-gap-report.json`)\n175: - `test-build-reports/`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\test-build-reports`)\n176: - `translation-quality-summary.md`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\translation-quality-summary.md`)\n177: - `translation-quality-summary.json`: present (`D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\translation-quality-summary.json`)\n178: - `kotlin-analysis/grad